## 5. 系統架構與整合

```
[開發者 / IDE] --> [Agent (Cursor/CLI)] --> [Skill Registry]
                                                   |
                   +-------------------------------+-------------------------------+
                   |                               |                               |
          [Skill: skeleton]            [Skill: config-gen]           [Skill: test-gen]
                   |                               |                               |
          [輸出: Java/YAML 檔]         [輸出: config.yml]            [輸出: Test.java]
                   |
          [Maven Build / Paper Server]
                   |
          [GitHub Actions CI/CD]
```

整合要點：
- **Skill Registry**：`skills-registry.yml` 集中管理所有 skill 的 ID、版本、入口 prompt 檔路徑
- **版本控制**：每個 Skill 以 semver 標記，存放於 `skills/<skill-name>/` 子目錄
- **執行環境**：Cursor Agent 或 CLI agent（Node.js/Python runner）
- **授權**：Skill 可標記 `public` / `team-only`，敏感 skill 需 token 驗證
- **安全考量**：Skill 輸入須白名單驗證，避免 prompt injection；不允許 Skill 直接執行 shell 命令
- **整合點**：產出檔案直接寫入專案目錄；CI/CD Skill 可觸發 GitHub Actions API

---

## 6. 資料格式與範例檔

### skills-registry.yml 範例
```yaml
version: "1.0.0"
skills:
  - id: generate-plugin-skeleton
    version: "1.2.0"
    description: 產生 Bukkit/Paper 插件 Maven 骨架
    prompt_file: skills/generate-plugin-skeleton/prompt.md
    schema_file: skills/generate-plugin-skeleton/schema.json
    tags: [scaffold, maven, bukkit]
    access: public

  - id: generate-config-yml
    version: "1.0.1"
    description: 產生結構化 config.yml
    prompt_file: skills/generate-config-yml/prompt.md
    schema_file: skills/generate-config-yml/schema.json
    tags: [config, yaml]
    access: public
```

### Skill 輸入 schema.json 範例
```json
{
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ["pluginName", "mcVersion", "author"],
  "properties": {
    "pluginName": { "type": "string", "minLength": 1 },
    "mcVersion":  { "type": "string", "pattern": "^\\d+\\.\\d+(\\.\\d+)?$" },
    "author":     { "type": "string" },
    "package":    { "type": "string", "default": "com.example" }
  }
}
```

